    {
      "id": "fgq5c34dxtt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 88,
      "y": 204,
      "width": 324,
      "height": 363,
      "strokeColor": "#3b5bdb",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "text": "🖥️ Web 管控面板\n\n/agents  树形配置 + 状态徽章\n/agents/:id/monitor  实时监控\n/agents/audit  全局审计页\n/agents/:id/optimization  Prompt审核\n/api-tools  API工具库管理\n\n人机协同通知面板\n铃铛图标·待确认列表\nSub: {userId}/notify\n\n管理员可代理响应任意\npending HITL 请求",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "5bxxc02dgtr",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
