    {
      "id": "vyie6ivwpvt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 448,
      "y": 404,
      "width": 314,
      "height": 163,
      "strokeColor": "#0b7285",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "text": "🤖 Agent Runner\n(Next.js 常驻进程)\n\nSub: agent/+/+/task/assign\nSub: agent/+/+/human/response\n> 调用 LLM 推理\n> 调用 MCP 工具\n> 调用 API 工具 (F-00b)\nPub: task/result | task/failed",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "t0cvs4f8cgr",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
