    {
      "id": "eedtjvzhwjt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 798,
      "y": 404,
      "width": 404,
      "height": 163,
      "strokeColor": "#868e96",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "text": "⚙️ Agent 生命周期状态机 (F-05)\n\nidle → running → waiting_human\n  ↓(human.response=approve)→ 恢复\n  ↓(human.response=reject) → error\n  ↓(超时 timeout_minutes)  → failed\n\n超时策略: 统一视为任务失败\n通过 MQTT task/failed 通知真人",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "4zw9xa3kx7r",
