    {
      "id": "tpac56t4uft",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1238,
      "y": 204,
      "width": 384,
      "height": 363,
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "text": "🔄 自我优化引擎 (F-11/F-12)\n\n触发 (满足任一):\n• 反馈累积 ≥ optimization_threshold\n• 每周 Cron Job 定期\n\n执行:\n① 读 agent_feedback_logs\n② LLM 分析 reject/modify 模式\n③ 生成新 Prompt 草稿\n④ 写 agent_prompt_versions(draft)\n⑤ Pub optimization/ready\n\n管理员审核:\n采纳 → status=active\nagents.system_prompt 自动更新\n\n反馈信号 (F-10):\napprove +1 · reject -1\nmodify ±diff · task_fail -1",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "64dpja1wj0r",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
