      "width": 314,
      "height": 363,
      "strokeColor": "#0c8599",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "text": "🗃️ PostgreSQL\n\nagents\n  tool_ids · api_tool_ids\n  optimization_threshold\n  current_prompt_version_id\n\nagent_tasks + task_runs\n\nagent_human_requests\n  status: pending/responded\n  /timeout/canceled\n\nagent_feedback_logs\n  signal_type, signal_value\n  before/after_data, context\n\nagent_prompt_versions\n  draft→active→retired\n\nagent_api_tools (F-00a)\n  url_template, auth_config(🔒)\n\nagent_trigger_keys (F-00c)\n  key_hash(SHA-256), scopes",
